Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.37,0:00:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.11,0:00:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角 追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.71,0:00:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.59,0:00:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.09,0:00:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.20,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.44,0:00:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.31,0:00:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.01,0:01:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.42,0:01:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.52,0:01:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.86,0:01:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.13,0:01:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.93,0:01:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.47,0:01:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.83,0:01:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（田所）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.42,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#03 週六夜晚與週日早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喲，荒卷，你能來真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能不來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慫恿總理叫我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是田所會長您啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼生氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從發生上次那件電子錢失竊案之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.05,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縣警和保全公司都不能信任了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，就請開門見山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓在下聽聽您有何貴幹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.22,0:03:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是...那個黑客的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，叫什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記得名字是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,CASH EYE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙昨天送了這張預告狀過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.34,0:04:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從那之後就決定用現金的方式保管我的全部財產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以現在我的全部財產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.55,0:04:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都鎖在這棟大樓的地下金庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.52,0:04:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從某個角度來說這也許是最安全的防衛手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之前也是這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.86,0:04:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，昨晚那傢伙遠距離操縱女性人造人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但輕鬆侵入這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.03,0:04:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還故意破壞防盜攝影機讓人發現她的犯罪行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再從50樓窗戶跳下去脫逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,物理上的防衛手段擋不住偷竊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她大概是來表達這個意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單單根據您所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.92,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這果然不是我們應該出面的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.79,0:05:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其依賴少數精銳的9課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.49,0:05:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如拿定主意，向人手充足的縣警報案才是明智之舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.53,0:05:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能那樣做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯罪預告的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.40,0:05:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是明天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.04,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將舉辦一場聚集了政經界大佬的某種秘密派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.35,0:05:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然這不是什麼不合法的派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是個人興趣性質的聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.15,0:05:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，也不能讓不識趣的人在會場上隨便亂晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.19,0:05:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且性質上這個派對無法更改會場或延長時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該知道才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時也會在這種地方處理國事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以需要通情達理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.27,0:05:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加強警備方面可以交給保全公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.58,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是問題出在現場指揮者的素質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.11,0:06:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然有上級的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.12,0:06:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我是不能拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.79,0:06:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很清楚總理為什麼會推薦你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以聞到白色血液的味道不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.26,0:06:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不是人造人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，泛用性的全身義體跟人造人一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.81,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠引發對無機性身體的慾望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.08,0:06:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺總理應該對他相當厭惡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故且不管個人的印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.35,0:06:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次行動是為了堅決推動無法如願進行的改革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.49,0:06:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了消滅前政權的亡靈這一招也是很正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.69,0:06:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人的怨念真是可怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.00,0:06:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是幫忙幹這種壞事我心裏也不太舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.27,0:06:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我也不認為這件工作值得我被迫放棄休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.11,0:07:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過明天還有一堆更氣人的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要做到一半忍不住發作喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看得到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看得到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，剛剛那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是阪華精機的董事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.61,0:07:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這些政經界有頭有臉的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然會瞞著夫人辦這種炫耀情趣娃娃的派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是出乎意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.19,0:07:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次換前外相登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.23,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是學不乖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甘拜下風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，課長和少校的座車也到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很精彩的畫面喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甘拜下風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，老爹那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是比預定計劃還要投入啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.59,0:08:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且少校她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.40,0:08:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很受那些變態歡迎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛屁股被摸了一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼不見為淨嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.81,0:08:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，進地下金庫的護照就交給少校負貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這邊也開始準備羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.78,0:08:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也到派對會場去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬，準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，等少校的信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷，你的判斷很正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常令人激賞的偽裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.68,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它部下也已經進入預定位置確保派對能順利進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警備狀態這麼嚴密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.38,0:09:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算小偷能進到金庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.35,0:09:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不認為她能把現金全部搬走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.19,0:09:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過之前也發生了那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.73,0:09:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你一定要抓到犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.33,0:09:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在犯罪預告時間來臨之前請你們繼續參加派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要去參觀一下實際狀況?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常樂意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川，狀況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情有點不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田所的地下金庫在幾天前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有可能增設了保安設備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然清查了製造商的服務器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.33,0:10:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是新施工部分的設計圖全部都已經銷毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們做了徹底的情報管制工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕只留下了書面資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.80,0:10:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校已經去採集田所的網膜和電子腦紋模型了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算能弄到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.91,0:10:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打不開最關鍵的那扇門一切都只是泡影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.98,0:10:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會想辦法從別的管道去找出開門的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.89,0:10:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.85,0:10:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也許會嘲笑這個興趣很怪異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.93,0:10:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，體驗過各種快樂的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後找到的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是對人偶的戀物癖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.17,0:10:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每一件都是著名設計師一塊一塊手工縫製的高級訂製服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.21,0:10:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體則與你的義體有著幾乎相同的機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有興趣跟其中一個交換看看啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，狀況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.02,0:11:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是很明顯的性騷擾喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.62,0:11:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知不覺老毛病就犯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乍看之下好像是泛用型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.20,0:11:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻連小地方都做的相當精緻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皮膚觸覺受器是16的平方嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在必須要忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪受得了什麼感覺都去接收啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就把感覺器官切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?要不要試試?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多該開始進行作戰計劃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想擁抱我沒有意識的身體?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.62,0:11:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你很瞭解我這種人的興趣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.66,0:11:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相反地你想不想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.33,0:11:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把有意識的人類當成人偶一樣來對待?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.98,0:12:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把感覺器官開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.15,0:12:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是身體一動也不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.26,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去要是引發心臟麻痹我可就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以接下來就在夢裏玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.54,0:12:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長，成功取得網膜和電子腦紋模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好，進入第二階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.01,0:12:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特、托古薩，你們那邊如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在開始行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.26,0:12:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，這裏是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.84,0:13:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田所先生特別吩咐我們過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,監視器切換完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹得好，塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.87,0:13:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.04,0:13:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來就是等少校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到手了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正都這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.46,0:14:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛入田所的電子腦中連他一起帶來不是比較快嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.34,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有別的事情需要他去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法切斷那個系統嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.13,0:14:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是獨立運作的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是硬把系統破壞掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就會被管理中心發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是什麼大問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下就是能不能打開金庫的門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算徹底調查過一遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.34,0:14:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我是從搬進田所大樓的建築材料規模
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.51,0:14:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來推算金庫的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.41,0:14:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，應該是刻意用四層舊式的鎖組合而成的機械密碼式金庫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.55,0:14:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是把田所一起帶來比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今已經不可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川，用B計劃怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.23,0:15:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以事前準備好的炸藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,足夠把金庫的支柱燒斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是到那時候我們的犯罪行動就會被發現喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.63,0:15:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一個問題在於
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算能炸破庫門到裏面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.61,0:15:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金庫後面不知道還有什麼機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不見得就沒有雙重防備喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不入虎穴焉得虎子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.28,0:15:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我們的目的不在盜取現金不必管這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.59,0:15:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，開始進行B計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.46,0:15:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，再過去我們就不能陪你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你的關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.71,0:15:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也去準備下一步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來您在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經這個時間啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派對呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.10,0:16:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預告的時間快要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.23,0:16:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然祈禱不要發生任何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長，請快到控制室來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是小偷潛進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬，準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.88,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時都0K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切換到自備發電機了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.28,0:17:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位來賓不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這畢竟是那種興趣的派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能發生任何意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.35,0:17:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以請按照我們的指示迅速離開現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是昨天那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是怎麼到那邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上叫部下過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她似乎想炸破金庫的門進去裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜無論如何她都是甕中之鱉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您的意思是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.88,0:17:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除我以外的人只要進入那個金庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙重防盜門就會關閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了用我擁有的靈魂鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.89,0:17:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對無法打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈魂鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先別管這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.37,0:18:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快去找出遠距離操縱她的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該要抓的是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.84,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來她要不是獨立AI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是擁有全身義體的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有任何接收遙控電波的跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就是黑客本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.42,0:18:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且剛剛又收到這張預告狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.10,0:18:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷，你馬上跟我一起到金庫去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.03,0:18:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親眼確認她是死於正當防衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金庫裏面會變成密封空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.28,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且在一定時間內製造出接近真空的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.65,0:18:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算她是義體人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.25,0:18:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不可能存活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長，少校她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.34,0:19:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到人了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我仔細搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉我遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.32,0:20:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為田所會長實在太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.23,0:20:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個...還好而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.86,0:20:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你是怎麼做到的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.23,0:20:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是叫塔奇克馬製造虛擬影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.37,0:20:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們以為我走進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來，田所會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.64,0:20:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.91,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏堆積的鈔票既然都在你的金庫裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.78,0:20:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該全都是您的東西沒錯吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.78,0:20:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在說些什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其做這種蠢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不如給我去找小偷的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田所會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.26,0:20:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們真正的目的是讓你自己打開這座金庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.40,0:20:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後確認裏面鈔票的流水號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.91,0:20:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們接到情報顯示您負責管理藥島前幹事長剩餘的隱匿財產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.98,0:21:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們做了這次秘密調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.02,0:21:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國稅局通緝中的流水號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.62,0:21:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個狀況下您恐怕無法辯解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.99,0:21:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來我們有很多事情想好好請教您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以請您跟我們走一趟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.97,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(我來查核了 國稅局查察部)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.61,0:21:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作請快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.74,0:21:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們那邊怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.98,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都先欲擒故縱放他們離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為要是能透過這些人順藤摸瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.95,0:21:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可能還有更多隱藏的金脈會浮出檯面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.56,0:21:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人都是大色狼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.93,0:21:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是有特殊嗜好的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前經濟團體聯合會會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據傳與政界有密切關係的田所勉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.08,0:22:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因涉嫌巨額逃稅以及洗錢遭到逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.92,0:22:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪盜遊戲也挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.39,0:22:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.06,0:22:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一瞬間我嚇出一身冷汗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.13,0:22:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想說少校該不會就那樣被做成真空包了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.07,0:22:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂團隊合作不是應該在事前把計劃告訴同伴嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.97,0:22:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.37,0:22:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盜賊這一行的鐵則可是騙人或者被騙喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.78,0:22:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還要在怪盜氣氛中沉迷到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.75,0:22:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作可是堆積如山啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.49,0:22:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是該認真考慮轉行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.71,0:23:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.38,0:23:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.82,0:23:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.86,0:23:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.16,0:23:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.73,0:23:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音——醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.80,0:23:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字——然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.88,0:23:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身——醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.31,0:23:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我——時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.75,0:23:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相，所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.12,0:23:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的——它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.92,0:24:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在軀殼裏的美麗
